        "TileImage": "$($repository 9e85c891-9eb7-4f3c-8115-896bf54d979b).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. I just got informed that Alma Reynard had survived our hit on her but the only reason she survived is because of your second target, Charlie Burke, an ex-doctor,  turned bodyguard for Alma Reynard. He was able to bring Reynard back to a stable condition and has been recently promoted. Time to go back and make sure that Reynard never returns again.",
